<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ถ้าเกิดไม่แฉสังคมจะดีขึ้น - หยุดวงเวียนทำลายชีวิต</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Chakra+Petch:wght@500;700&family=Mitr:wght@400;600&family=Sarabun:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0b0813;
            --panel-bg: #141122;
            --text-main: #e2daf8;
            --text-muted: #8c81ad;
            --red-alert: #ff3333;
            --gold-warn: #ffd700;
            --blue-law: #00e5ff;
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            word-spacing: -0.5px;
            letter-spacing: -0.1px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px 10px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding-bottom: 20px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-family: 'Mitr', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        header .subtitle {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--gold-warn);
